I"¬<h2 id="summary">Summary</h2>

<p>A <em>subject</em> is composed of <em>questions</em>.</p>

<p>Subjects can be associated with a <em>course</em>. A course
is just a way of grouping subjects into topics.</p>

<p>An <em>assignment</em> is the instance of a subject for a given audience (a class or group of learners).
Learners always respond to the questions of a subject by signing up for the assignment that concerns them.</p>
